(14, 'Md.Manirul Islam', 'Mohan', 1915985336, 'fiforeg@gmail.com', 'Bali Magic Tour 5Days 4Nights', '12', '&lt;p&gt;ITINERARY :&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Day 01 : ARRIVAL BALI &amp;ndash; TRANSFER HOTEL&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Upon arrive at Ngurah Rai International Airport Denpasar &amp;ndash; Bali. Meet and Greet then transfer to the hotel for check in.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Day 02 : KINTAMANI - UBUD TOUR (B/L/D)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Breakfast at hotel, Morning tour you will be introduced to many varied faces of Bali. Tour will begin with the traditional Barong Dance, then you will visit the village of celuk, famous of its gold and silver work, the village MAS, a wood carving center, the village of Banjar Compound, an artist colony handicraft center at Ubud, a secret holy spring temple at Tampak Siring, Reaching kintamani village, perched on the rim of Batur Volcanic basin, overlooking lush panorama of lake &amp;amp; Mt Batur while enjoy your Buffet Lunch at the Kintamani Restaurant. On the way back, your guide will take you to local, plantation which rich with its herbs and coffee plans. then continue to Kuta Beach for free leisure&amp;nbsp;OR&amp;nbsp;if still have enough time you could take and Join Optional Tours of Uluwatu Temple (additional charges).&amp;nbsp;Dinner set menu served at Local Restaurant.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Day 03 : BEDUGUL - TANAH LOT TOUR (B/L/D)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Breakfast at hotel, Morning tour you will begin to visit Bedugul resort presenting fruit market, Ulun Danu Temple of a temple in the middle of Lake Bratan. Buffet Lunch at a Labagha Restaurant with many choices of Balinese Traditional Food. Tour continues to Tanah Lot Temple perched on a rocky outcrop in the sea situated at southwest part of Bali until Sunset&amp;nbsp;OR&amp;nbsp;if still have enough time you could take and Join Optional Tours of Bali Trick Eye Museum 3D (additional charges). Dinner set menu served at Local Restaurant.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Day 04 : TANJUNG BENOA BEACH TURTLE ISLAND &amp;ndash; SHOPPING (B/L/D)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Breakfast at hotel, Our tour Guide will pick you up at lobby around&amp;nbsp;10 AM&amp;nbsp;then tour will begin to visit Tanjung Benoa Beach to have Glass Bottom Boat and Turtle Island. And also you can enjoy another water sport activities such as : Parasailing, Banana Boat, Jet Ski, Snorkeling, Sea Walker, etc (water sport by own expenses). Lunch set menu served at Local Restaurant. Shopping program at Joger &amp;ndash; Bali Tshirt and Krisna/Hawaii shop&amp;nbsp;OR&amp;nbsp;if still have enough time you could take and Join Optional Romantic Sunset Dinner Cruise (additional charges for Up grade meals from Local Restaurant). Dinner set menu served at Local Restaurant.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Day 05 : DEPARTURE (B)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Breakfast at hotel. Free program own guest leisure OR until latest check out time (12 PM),&amp;nbsp;then 03 Hours before Departure Flight will pick up at Lobby Hotel for transfer out.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Special Note:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This Package is design with Economy Class Air fare ( Depends on availability ).&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AirTicket Price Can Change Any Time &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This Price Not Valid For Eid Time, christmas Time, Puja Time , 15th December to 10th January New Year , Any Special Holiday&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Includes :&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;* Hotel Accommodation, Transfer and Admission as