(63, 3, '2N THIMPU- 1N PARO', '&lt;p&gt;Day 01: PARO AIRPORT-THIMPU (60KM/2HOURS)&lt;br /&gt;Tourists will be received at Paro Airport. Visit Museum, Airport View Point &amp;amp; Transfer to Thimphu Hotel. It\'s 1 hour scenic drive. After having lunch visit Archery Ground,. In the evening strolling/shopping. After having dinner night halt at Hotel. Overnight Thimpu.&lt;br /&gt;Breakfast (No) Lunch (Yes) Dinner (Yes)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Day 02: THIMPU LOCAL SIGHT SEEING &lt;br /&gt;After Breakfast Thimpu city sightseeing. National Memorial Chorten, Royal Palace, Bhutan Parliament, Archery Ground, Local Market. BBS Tower etc. Evening a stroll in &amp;amp; around The Clock Tower. Overnight Thimpu.&lt;br /&gt;Breakfast (Yes) Lunch (Yes) Dinner (Yes)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Day 03: THIMPU-PARO &amp;amp; PARO SIGHTSEEING &lt;br /&gt;After having breakfast drive to Paro. Check in the hotel &amp;amp; visit Takshang Monastery from valley floor. Check in the Hotel. After lunch Visit Paro Dzong. In the evening free. Dinner &amp;amp; night halt at Hotel, overnight Paro.&lt;br /&gt;Breakfast (Yes) Lunch (Yes) Dinner (Yes)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Day 04: PARO AIRPORT &lt;br /&gt;After Breakfast proceed towards Paro airport. (Trip ends) &lt;br /&gt;Breakfast (Yes)&lt;/p&gt;', 'upload/9228e3b2cc.jpg', 'Sabbir Ahmed', 'bhutan Tour coast , bhutan tourism site', '2018-06-12 11:12:58', 5),
(64, 5, '7DAYS/6NIGHTS   BALI - JAKARTA TOUR', '&lt;p&gt;BASED ON SUN BOUTIQUE KUTA 3* BALI &amp;amp; BIG HOTEL KARTINI 3* JAKARTA&lt;br /&gt; ITINERARY :&lt;br /&gt;Day 01 : 20 Feb ARRIVAL BALI &amp;ndash; TRANSFER HOTEL&lt;br /&gt;Upon arrive at Ngurah Rai International Airport Denpasar &amp;ndash; Bali. Meet and Greet then transfer to the hotel for check in. &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;Day 02 : 21 Feb KINTAMANI - UBUD TOUR (B/L/D)&lt;br /&gt;Breakfast at hotel, Morning tour you will be introduced to many varied faces of Bali. Tour will begin with the traditional Barong Dance, then you will visit the village of celuk, famous of its gold and silver work, the village MAS, a wood carving center, the village of Banjar Compound, an artist colony handicraft center at Ubud, a secret holy spring temple at Tampak Siring, Reaching kintamani village, perched on the rim of Batur Volcanic basin, overlooking lush panorama of lake &amp;amp; Mt Batur while enjoy your Buffet Lunch at the Kintamani Restaurant. On the way back, your guide will take you to local, plantation which rich with its herbs and coffee plans. then continue to Kuta Beach for free leisure OR if still have enough time you could take and Join Optional Tours of Uluwatu Temple (additional charges). Dinner set menu served at Local Restaurant.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;Day 03 : 22 Feb BEDUGUL - TANAH LOT TOUR (B/L/D)&lt;br /&gt;Breakfast at hotel, Morning tour you will begin to visit Bedugul resort presenting fruit market, Ulun Danu Temple of a temple in the middle of Lake Bratan. Buffet Lunch at a Labagha Restaurant with many choices of Balinese Traditional Food. Tour continues to Tanah Lot Temple perched on a rocky outcrop in the sea situated at southwest part of Bali until Sunset OR if still have enough time you could take and Join Optional Tours of Bali Trick Eye Museum 3D (additional charges). Dinner set menu served at Local Restaurant. &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;Day 04 : 23 Feb TANJUNG BENOA BEACH TURTLE ISLAND &amp;ndash; SHOPPING (B/L/D)&lt;br /&gt;Breakfast at hotel, Our tour Guide will pick you up at lobby around 10 AM then tour will begin to visit Tanjung Benoa Beach to have Glass Bottom Boat and Turtle Island. And also you can enjoy another water sport activities such as : Parasailing, Banana Boat, Jet Ski, Snorkeling, Sea Walker, etc (water sport by own expenses). Lunch set menu served at Local Restaurant. Shopping program at Joger &amp;ndash; Bali Tshirt and Krisna/Hawaii shop OR if still have enough time you could take and Join Optional Romantic Sunset Dinner Cruise (additional charges for Up grade meals from Local Restaurant). Dinner set menu served at Local Restaurant.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;Day 05: 24 Feb DEPARTURE - FLIGHT TO JAKARTA (B)&lt;br /&gt;Breakfast at hotel. then pick up from Lobby Hotel Departure at 1050am &amp;amp; Arrival jakarta,At 11.45am meet and greet with our tour guide. Transfer to hotel for check in &amp;amp; free movement. Over night Hotel.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;Day 06: 25 Feb JAKARTA FULLDAY TOUR(B/L/D)&lt;br /&gt;Breakfast at hotel, visit TMII or miniature park, proceed to Museum Indonesia, cable car, shopping at ITC Mangga dua,Photostop at National Monument, presidential palace, Istiqlal Mosque, Chatedral church. Over night Hotel.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;Day 07: 26 Feb JAKARTA OUT(B)&lt;br /&gt;Breakfast at hotel. Free program own guest leisure OR until latest check out time (12 PM), then 03 Hours before Departure Flight will pick up at Lobby Hotel for transfer out. End of the services&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;Remarks :&lt;br /&gt;* Rates quote net per person, based on PRIVATE coach basis&lt;br /&gt;* Valid for low season only and high season surcharge will applied during Idul Fitri/Christmas/New years period&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;Includes :&lt;br /&gt;* Hotel Accommodation, Transfer and Admission as Itinerary&lt;br /&gt;* All tour &amp;amp; transfer on private basis&lt;br /&gt;* Professional English Speaking Tour Guide&lt;br /&gt;* Daily breakfast at hotel&lt;br /&gt;* Meals as per itinerary&lt;br /&gt;* Daily 01 bottle of mineral water during tour per person&lt;br /&gt;* Starter pack GSM local sim card (no credit)&lt;br /&gt;* Peak season surcharge in Bali during New Year period&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;Excludes :&lt;br /&gt;* International OR Domestic Airline&lt;br /&gt;* Optional Tour, Upgrading room, Meals for Lunch/Dinner and Beverages at the restaurant if any.&lt;br /&gt;* Tipping for Local Guide + Driver (suggestion at USD 3.00/pax/day)&lt;br /&gt;* Personal Expenses eg. Minibar, Telephone, Laundry, Porter, etc. Are not mentioned above&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;7DAYS/6NIGHTS BALI - JAKARTA TOUR&lt;br /&gt; BASED ON HOTEL SUN BOUTIQUE KUTA 3* BALI &amp;amp; BIG HOTEL KARTINI 3* JAKARTA&lt;br /&gt;Type of room : Superior room &amp;amp; Deluxe city view&lt;/p&gt;', 'upload/f2a0f05cf6.jpg', 'Mona', 'pattaya tour coast from bangladesh, tour company in bangladesh', '2018-06-12 11:16:38', 9),
