(69, 1, 'Darjeeling Tour 6 Days 5 nights', '&lt;table style=&quot;width: 690px;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;tr&gt;\r\n&lt;td width=&quot;690&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DAY 01: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TOWARDS INDIA FROM DHAKA. (430KM/8 HOURS).&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Start your journey from Dhaka Kalyanpur Bus counter. Dinner&amp;nbsp; break at Food Village&amp;nbsp; Bogra. Overnight bus journey.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Breakfast (No) | Lunch (No) | &amp;nbsp;Dinner (No)&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DAY 02: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;S.R. SHYAMOLI COUNTER --DARJEELING (ABOUT 80 KMS / 3 HRS)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Meet &amp;amp; Greet on arrival at Burimari Border&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; Assistance in immigration.&amp;nbsp; Enter India &amp;amp; Board Shyamoli Bus. Receive from Shyamoli bus counter. Lunch break at Siliguri &amp;amp; proceed towards Darjeeling which is one of the most magnificent hill resorts in the world&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; Evening free to explore this Hill Queen. (walking tour of Mall is suggested) .&lt;strong&gt;Overnight Halt Darjeeling.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Breakfast (No) | Lunch (Yes) | Dinner (Yes)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&lt;tr&gt;\r\n&lt;td width=&quot;690&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DAY 03: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SIGHT SEEING AT DARJEELING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; After Breakfast proceed for Mixed Points sightseeing including Japanese Temple, Peace Pagoda, Ava Art gallery, Rock Garden,&amp;nbsp; HMI, Zoo, Tenzing Rock, Tea garden&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;etc&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; Evening free at the Mall &amp;amp; market. &lt;strong&gt;Overnight Darjeeling.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Breakfast (Yes) | Lunch (Yes) | Dinner (Yes)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&lt;tr&gt;\r\n&lt;td width=&quot;690&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DAY 04: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DARJEELING Shiliguri.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Early morning 04.00am visit Tiger Hill to view Mt. Kanchanzungha, also Batasia Loop- War memorial &amp;amp; Ghoom Monastery&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; Come back at Hotel and Breakfast.09.00.am&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&lt;tr&gt;\r\n&lt;td width=&quot;690&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;After breakfast transfer to Mirrik. Enjoy Nepal Border on the way. Boating in Mirrik Lake (optional). Lunch at Siliguri.&amp;nbsp; After lunch full day free movement and shopping by Guest Cost. &lt;strong&gt;Overnight Shiliguri.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Breakfast (Yes) | Lunch (Yes) | Dinner (Yes)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DAY 05: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Morning &amp;nbsp;Breakfast &amp;nbsp;free movement and shopping by guest cost . After lunch to Shyamoli Bus counter for onward journey to Dhaka. Indian Exit &amp;amp; Bangladesh Entry. Dinner break at Food Village, Bogra. &lt;strong&gt;Overnight bus journey.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Breakfast (Yes) | Lunch (Yes) | Dinner (No)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&lt;tr&gt;\r\n&lt;td width=&quot;690&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DAY 06: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RECAH DHAKA.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Reach Dhaka&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;in the morning ( Tour Ends)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Special Note:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: under